Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.92,0:15:48.96,Faqi,,0,0,0,,Assault Form{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}天翔形態
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.41,0:15:55.72,Faqi,,0,0,0,,Schwertform{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}神劍形態
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.26,0:16:10.26,Default1,,0,0,0,,{\t(\bord4\3c&H00BBBB&)}雷子──
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.47,0:16:15.18,Default1,,0,0,0,,{\t(\bord4\3c&H8963696&)}飛龍──
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.18,0:16:18.17,Default1,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\3c&H00BBBB&}──震破
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.40,0:16:23.37,Default1,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\3c&H8963696&}──一閃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.34,0:16:54.00,Default1,,0,0,0,,既然你也是使役魔──「守護獸」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.95,0:16:58.53,Default1,,0,0,0,,為什麼不去糾正主人的錯誤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.13,0:17:01.97,Default1,,0,0,0,,「闇之書」的蒐集是我們的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.71,0:17:08.06,Default1,,0,0,0,,我們的主人對我們的蒐集毫不知情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.61,0:17:09.52,Default1,,0,0,0,,你說什麼…？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.28,0:17:11.52,Default1,,0,0,0,,這是怎麼一回事！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.19,0:17:17.29,Default1,,0,0,0,,為了主人 我們不惜身陷血海
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.85,0:17:19.76,Default1,,0,0,0,,與我同類的守護之獸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.42,0:17:22.60,Default1,,0,0,0,,妳不也是一樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.88,0:17:26.23,Default1,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.93,0:17:27.68,Default1,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.30,0:17:29.39,Default1,,0,0,0,,可是…！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.87,0:17:39.00,Default1,,0,0,0,,希格娜姆他們…！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:40.14,Default1,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.59,0:17:42.40,Default1,,0,0,0,,正在沙漠中交戰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.95,0:17:46.10,Default1,,0,0,0,,對手是泰斯塔羅莎與她的守護獸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.28,0:17:50.00,Default1,,0,0,0,,拖得太久恐怕會有麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.55,0:17:51.74,Default1,,0,0,0,,我去為他們助陣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.51,0:18:03.38,Default1,,0,0,0,,維塔？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.78,0:18:04.68,Default1,,0,0,0,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:06.28,Default1,,0,0,0,,我這裡也來追兵了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.91,0:18:08.19,Default1,,0,0,0,,是那個白衣的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.15,0:18:10.69,Default1,,0,0,0,,高町什麼的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.49,0:18:14.40,Default1,,0,0,0,,是「奈葉」！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:16.65,Default1,,0,0,0,,奈{\fnsimhei}·{\r}葉！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.31,0:18:24.96,Default1,,0,0,0,,維塔… 我們就不能談一談嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.76,0:18:27.21,Default1,,0,0,0,,說不定…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.55,0:18:32.15,Default1,,0,0,0,,我們還可以幫助你們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:38.23,Default1,,0,0,0,,囉嗦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.83,0:18:42.18,Default1,,0,0,0,,誰會相信管理局的花言巧語啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.58,0:18:45.88,Default1,,0,0,0,,我不是管理局的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.17,0:18:48.59,Default1,,0,0,0,,是民間協助者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.79,0:18:55.47,Default1,,0,0,0,,「闇之書」對每位魔導師只能蒐集一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.89,0:18:59.77,Default1,,0,0,0,,就算戰勝她 也得不到書頁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.50,0:19:03.77,Default1,,0,0,0,,現在也不是浪費魔力彈的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.54,0:19:06.59,Default1,,0,0,0,,維塔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.23,0:19:10.88,Default1,,0,0,0,,等我下次再來收拾妳！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.82,0:19:15.71,Default1,,0,0,0,,怒吼吧 鋼鐵伯爵！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.25,0:19:17.56,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\t(\bord4\3c&H81111EE&)}Eisengeheul{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}鋼鐵咆哮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.52,0:19:29.28,Default1,,0,0,0,,逃脫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.79,0:19:38.75,Faqi,,0,0,0,,Master.{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}主人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.82,0:19:42.51,Default1,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.91,0:19:45.20,Default1,,0,0,0,,距離這麼遠 不會再遭到攻擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.10,0:19:48.40,Default1,,0,0,0,,{\t(\bord4\3c&H81111EE&)}次元傳送
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.30,0:19:52.42,Faqi,,0,0,0,,Buster mode{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}烈魄模式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.78,0:19:54.10,Faqi,,0,0,0,,Drive ignition{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}魔導驅動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.67,0:19:59.26,Default1,,0,0,0,,準備好!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.53,0:20:01.90,Default1,,0,0,0,,來一次久違的遠距離炮擊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.67,0:20:03.97,Faqi,,0,0,0,,Load cartridge{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}魔力彈裝填
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.93,0:20:09.58,Default1,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.29,0:20:12.90,Default1,,0,0,0,,要從那麼遠發射嗎！？
