Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.34,0:20:33.32,Default1,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\3c&H88000BB&}──烈破
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.79,0:20:36.33,Default1,,0,0,0,,不會吧！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.14,0:20:48.64,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fs66}命中目標
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.14,0:20:48.64,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's a direct hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.91,0:20:51.56,Default1,,0,0,0,,是不是有些下手太重了…？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.89,0:20:53.39,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fs66}就應該這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.89,0:20:53.39,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.66,0:21:05.50,Default1,,0,0,0,,你是什麼人…？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.18,0:21:06.66,Default1,,0,0,0,,快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.50,0:21:10.73,Default1,,0,0,0,,不是要完成「闇之書」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.51,0:21:19.29,Default1,,0,0,0,,{\t(\bord4\3c&H88000BB&)}天神──
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.21,0:21:23.26,Faqi,,0,0,0,,Master!{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}主人！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.89,0:21:27.69,Default1,,0,0,0,,枷鎖…！？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.93,0:21:29.00,Default1,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.67,0:21:32.19,Default1,,0,0,0,,一瞬間從那麼遠的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.16,0:21:46.82,Faqi,,0,0,0,,Sorry, master.{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}主人 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.92,0:21:50.47,Default1,,0,0,0,,不… 都怪我太大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.26,0:22:11.69,Default1,,0,0,0,,戰鬥持續許久 卻依然如此敏捷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.72,0:22:14.80,Default1,,0,0,0,,某些攻擊已超越我的眼力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.97,0:22:17.75,Default1,,0,0,0,,必須速戰速決才行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.29,0:22:27.06,Default1,,0,0,0,,好強…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.69,0:22:31.87,Default1,,0,0,0,,近距戰與中距戰都完全處於下風
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.77,0:22:34.95,Default1,,0,0,0,,現在僅有靠速度維持局勢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.92,0:22:38.56,Default1,,0,0,0,,只要中招一次 便會立刻被擊潰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.87,0:22:44.99,Default1,,0,0,0,,「烈風蒼鷹」… 能擊中她嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.68,0:22:49.06,Default1,,0,0,0,,「超音形態」… 這是唯一的選擇了…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.25,0:23:12.20,Default1,,0,0,0,,泰斯塔羅莎…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.21,0:23:19.86,Default1,,0,0,0,,你這傢伙！！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.01,0:23:34.31,Default1,,0,0,0,,來吧 快奪去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.17,0:25:12.41,Default1,,0,0,0,,菲特的「念動之核」被奪走了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.73,0:25:14.04,Default1,,0,0,0,,「阿斯拉」返回了我們的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.55,0:25:17.26,Default1,,0,0,0,,但是 事件卻越發撲朔迷離
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.97,0:25:21.52,Default1,,0,0,0,,尤諾君揭開了「闇之書」過去的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.29,0:25:26.30,Default1,,0,0,0,,下集 魔法少女奈葉A's 第8話
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.74,0:25:29.80,Default1,,0,0,0,,悲哀的決意、勇氣的抉擇
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.18,0:25:32.03,Default1,,0,0,0,,魔導驅動！！
